<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />Therefore his people turn to them</para>

<para style="q1">and abundant waters are drained out.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />They say, "How does God know?</para>

<para style="q1">Is there knowledge with the Most High?"</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />Take notice: these people are wicked;</para>

<para style="q1">they are always carefree, becoming richer and richer.</para>
